name: accelerate
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "accelerate" %}
{% set version = "0.12.0" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/accelerate-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e8b119c94fac31877620d5f9de311164ec81fa9dc9e175f0d0d4f50fc8d79473

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  entry_points:
    - accelerate=accelerate.commands.accelerate_cli:main
    - accelerate-config=accelerate.commands.config:main
    - accelerate-launch=accelerate.commands.launch:main
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - numpy >=1.17
    - packaging >=20.0
    - psutil
    - pytorch >=1.4.0
    - python >=3.6
    - pyyaml

test:
  imports:
    - accelerate
    - accelerate.commands
  commands:
    - pip check
    - accelerate --help
    - accelerate-config --help
    - accelerate-launch --help
  requires:
    - datasets
    - pip
    - sentencepiece
    - transformers

about:
  home: https://github.com/huggingface/accelerate
  doc_url: https://huggingface.co/docs/accelerate
  summary: Training loop of PyTorch without boilerplate code
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - thewchan
